IUD Insertion status values

Codes representing possible values for the IUD Insertion status element

  • Include these codes as defined in http://hl7.org/fhir/event-status
    CodeDisplay
    completedIUD Insertion completedThe event has now concluded.
    not-doneIUD Insertion not possibleThe event was terminated prior to any activity beyond preparation. I.e. The 'main' activity has not yet begun. The boundary between preparatory and the 'main' activity is context-specific.
